hey this is my poemy

Zindagi ki raahon mein,
Kabhi kabhi thakan ho jaye,
Par khud ko haar mat manna,
Nayi umeedon ka jahan banaaye.

Har subah suraj ki kirnon se,
Apne sapno ko jagayein,
Har raat chaand ke saaye mein,
Apni khwahishon ko sajayein.

Dil se nikli har dhadkan,
Ek nayi kahani sunaye,
Har mushkil ka samna karte,
Aur khud ko bulandiyon tak layein.
